 that jet solution are achieved at all\nmagnetization level, while winds could be obtained only in weakly magnetized\ndisks that feature heating.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Sep 2019 17:08:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2019 21:39:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-16"}
