e overall spectral\nproperties of the NHH and the corresponding Liouvillian for a given system can\ndiffer substantially, their LEPs and HEPs occur for the same combination of\nsystem parameters.}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Sep 2019 17:35:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2019 16:40:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2020 12:56:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-16"}
