e this problem with a non-linear generalization of the\ncausal linear thermodynamics of bulk viscosity and also with the inclusion of\nsome form of dark energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Sep 2019 22:20:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-17"}
