nstrated they are highly correlated. This indicates that the numerically\nreconstructed holograms rendered on a light field or 2D display have a high\npredictive value for the perceived quality on holographic display.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2019 10:13:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-30"}
