uperconducting quantum\ninterference device indicating the coupling of the electric field with\nthesuperconducting phase. Among the possible applications of the presented\nphenomenology, we conclude this review by proposing some devices that may\nrepresent a breakthrough in superconducting quantum and classical computation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2019 14:48:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 08:29:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
